Package: fdid
Type: Package
Title: Factorial Difference-in-Differences
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2025-06-20
Authors@R:
    c(person("Rivka", "Lipkovitz", email = "rivkal@mit.edu", role = c("aut")),
      person("Yiqing", "Xu", , "yiqingxu@stanford.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: Implements the factorial difference-in-differences (FDID) framework for panel data with multi-period or staggered treatments. Provides OLS (with / without interactions), DID, entropy balancing, and augmented IPW estimators; supports robust, bootstrap, and jackknife variance; returns dynamic, pre/event/post aggregates and raw means; and includes helpers for data preparation and plotting.
    Methodology follows Xu, Zhao & Ding (2024) <arXiv:2407.11937>.
URL: https://github.com/xuyiqing/fdid
